===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# {{countable}} A [[specific]] act committed in [[violation]] of the [[law]].
# {{uncountable}} The [[practice]] or [[habit]] of [[commit]]ting crimes.
#: '''''Crime''' doesn’t pay.''

